---
title: Golden Halloumi and Ratatouille with Roasted Garlic Dressing and Ciabatta
description: The combination of roasted veggies and garlic dressing with seared halloumi makes this a classic vegetarian dinner for any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/haloumi-dore-et-ratatouille-ac45ef8c.jpg
